FROST, Appellant, v. WEEHAWKEN WHARF CO., Respondent. (City Court of New York,

General Term.

October 29, 1900.) Action by Eelihu B. Frost, as assignee, against the Weehawken Wharf Company. From an order the plaintiff appeals. Affirmed. Norman-G. Johnson, for appellant. Wilder & Anderson, for respondent. PER CURIAM.

Order appealed from affirmed, with costs.
